Sentencas: A novel porous cathode of LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 perovskite with aligned porosities was engineered for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Fabrication of aligned porous LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 perovskite by water based freeze casting

Sentencas: LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 was produced through metal nitrate and acid citric combustion method and calcined at different temperatures.
Titulo: Fabrication of aligned porous LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 perovskite by water based freeze casting

Sentencas: The synthesized LNF at 600 degrees C shows specific surface area (S-BET) of 24.4 m(2)g (1) and an average pore size of 12.2 nm.
Titulo: Fabrication of aligned porous LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 perovskite by water based freeze casting

Sentencas: The chemical composition and structure of LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 synthesized at temperature 600-1400 degrees C, were analyzed by XRD, XPS and HRTEM. SEM observations of freeze cast nano-sized LNF showed the vertically aligned hexagonal walls.
Titulo: Fabrication of aligned porous LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 perovskite by water based freeze casting

Sentencas: These walls contain a great value of fine pores which accelerate the gas transportation.
Titulo: Fabrication of aligned porous LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 perovskite by water based freeze casting
